Description: Dof ASA is a Norway-based provider of essential offshore and subsea services to the global offshore industry. DOF ASA is the holding Company for the DOF Group. The Company operates in three segments of the offshore services market, strategically defined by activities and vessel types: Platform Supply Vessels (PSV), Anchor Handling Tug Supply vessels (AHTS), and Subsea vessels and Subsea engineering services (Subsea). Dofâ€™s fleet comprises nearly 60 purpose-built offshore vessels that have an engineering capacity to service the offshore energy market. The vessels include Skandi Ipanema, Skandi Hera, Skandi Hugen, as well Skandi Commander. The Company has several subsidiaries, including DOF Management AS, Marin IT AS, DOF Subsea AS and DOF UK Ltd.
